readable.content: a brown dog and a white dog are running across a stony hillock . Two brown and white dogs , one a boxer and the other a terrier , play on a rock covered hill with a blue sky and powdery clouds in the background . Two brown and white dogs run on rocks , sky in background . Two dogs are running along a rocky hill . Two dogs run next to each other across rough terrain .
